<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Você foi convidado — LogCell</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Syne:wght@700;800&display=swap');

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      background-color: #0d0f14;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      color: #e8eaf0;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .wrapper {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 0 32px;
    }

    .logo {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #06b6d4);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .logo-text {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #ffffff;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    /* Card */
    .card {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #161a24, #111520);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }

    .card-top {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a5f 0%, #0f2744 50%, #0a1628 100%);
      padding: 48px 48px 40px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card-top::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -60px;
      right: -60px;
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,130,246,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .card-top::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -40px;
      left: 30%;
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(6,182,212,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      background: rgba(59,130,246,0.2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.3);
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 5px 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #93c5fd;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .badge::before {
      content: '';
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      background: #3b82f6;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .headline {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .subheadline {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      line-height: 1.6;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* Body */
    .card-body {
      padding: 40px 48px;
    }

    .invited-by {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .invited-avatar {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #06b6d4);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: white;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .invited-info {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .invited-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .invited-name {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #e8eaf0;
    }

    .message {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .message strong {
      color: #e8eaf0;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Role badge */
    .role-box {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: rgba(6,182,212,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(6,182,212,0.2);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .role-icon {
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .role-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    }

    .role-name {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #67e8f9;
    }

    /* CTA Button */
    .cta-wrap {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #2563eb);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 16px 48px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(59,130,246,0.35), 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .expiry {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      margin: 0 0 28px;
    }

    .fallback {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .fallback a {
      color: #60a5fa;
      text-decoration: none;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 0 48px;
    }

    .footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">
        <div class="logo-mark">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M4 10h12M10 4v12" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="logo-text">LogCell</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="badge">Convite exclusivo</div>
        <div class="headline">Você foi<br>convidado.</div>
        <div class="subheadline">Acesse a plataforma de gestão da sua loja</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="invited-by">
          <% inviter = @resource.invited_by %>
          <div class="invited-avatar"><%= inviter&.name&.first&.upcase || "?" %></div>
          <div class="invited-name"><%= inviter&.name || "Administrador" %></div>
        </div>

        <p class="message">
          Olá, <strong><%= @resource.name %></strong>!<br><br>
          Você foi convidado para acessar o <strong>LogCell</strong>, o sistema de gestão da sua loja.
          Clique no botão abaixo para criar sua senha e começar a usar a plataforma.
        </p>

        <% if @resource.groups.any? %>
        <div class="role-box">
          <div class="role-icon">🔑</div>
          <div>
            <div class="role-label">Seu perfil de acesso</div>
            <div class="role-name"><%= @resource.groups.map(&:name).join(", ") %></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% end %>

        <div class="cta-wrap">
          <%= link_to "Criar minha senha →", accept_user_invitation_url(invitation_token: @token), class: "cta-btn" %>
        </div>

        <p class="expiry">⏳ Este link expira em 7 dias</p>

        <hr class="divider">

        <p class="fallback">
          Se o botão não funcionar, copie e cole este link no seu navegador:<br>
          <a href="<%= accept_user_invitation_url(invitation_token: @token) %>">
            <%= accept_user_invitation_url(invitation_token: @token) %>
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        LogCell · Sistema de Gestão<br>
        Você recebeu este email pois foi convidado por um administrador.<br>
        Se não reconhece este convite, ignore este email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
